        {
            "title": "上海驚現「24/8 FITNESS」山寨健身室　網民：一周有8日？｜網上熱話",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"上海驚現疑似山寨版24/7 FITNESS，名叫「24/8 FITNESS」。(小紅書圖)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"617\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/2Y_0ejBeMymZOJw.kJ7vgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/f3ea67a4a4e9284c0d351d7a042db375\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">上海驚現疑似山寨版24/7 FITNESS，名叫「24/8 FITNESS」。(小紅書圖)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近日上海出現一家名為「24/8 FITNESS」的健身中心，其名稱與標誌設計與香港連鎖健身品牌「<span>24/7 FITNESS</span>」高度相似，迅速在網路上引發熱議。這家健身中心透過小紅書平台積極推廣，然而其獨特的名稱卻讓眾多網友感到困惑，紛紛質疑這是否為又一宗山寨抄襲案例。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">官方指「8」代表8小時睡<span><span><span>眠</span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原本24/7 FITNESS品牌中的數字「7」代表一個星期7日，意為中心全日24小時開放。但對於「24/8」的名稱，惹來網民不解和追問。對此，官方解釋<span><span><span>一天除了8小時的睡眠時間，其他時間都可以用來健身，並且在</span></span></span>小紅書上解釋：<span><span><span>「一天24小時，8小時健康充足睡眠，8小時健體精力充沛，8小時建設美好生活。」</span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-93899f7d-5f12-3cac-843c-7d27e261e92b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span>然而，不少網民對於</span></span></span>「24/8 FITNESS」名稱仍然不買單，在其官方小紅書帳戶留言：<span><span><span><span><span>「山寨健身房」、「名字也是抄襲，想問也是用山寨機械嗎？」、「你們和247是啥關係？」、「來你那裡可以一周有8天？」</span></span></span></span></span>更有網友提問「會告24/7抄襲？然後要247賠錢」，暗指<span><span><span><span><span>當年喬丹品牌、無印良品等在內地</span></span></span></span></span>商標爭議事件。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>「24/7」CEO：研升級去24/9</span></span></span></span></span></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">面對<span><span><span><span><span>疑似品牌</span></span></span></span></span>遭抄襲的情況<span><span><span><span><span>，「24/7 FITNESS」行政總裁黃靜怡已在個人IG亦發帖文回應，笑言「同事們係時間研究升級去24/9」。此前黃靜怡透露，這兩年來投資近2億人民幣進軍上海市場，目標在今年底增至32間分店。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/上海驚現-24-8-fitness-山寨健身室-網民-一周有8日-網上熱話/605497?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/上海驚現-24-8-fitness-山寨健身室-網民-一周有8日-網上熱話/605497?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/上海驚現-24-8-fitness-山寨健身室-網民-一周有8日-網上熱話/605497?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%A9%9A%E7%8F%BE-24-8-fitness-%E5%B1%B1%E5%AF%A8%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E5%AE%A4-071500022.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 15:40:46",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "香港隔夜融資成本料將降至3% 因聯儲會降息及貸款放緩",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 在聯儲會料將降息且貸款需求疲軟下，香港隔夜借貸成本到年底前可能降至3%左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">星展銀行預測，1個月期銀行同業拆息(Hibor)將降至2.5%左右，華僑銀行則預期該利率會接近3%。受股市資金流入和IPO熱潮的影響，Hibor在9月的季度出現近30年來的最大上漲；在上周超級強颱「樺加沙」襲擊香港後資金需求放緩，該利率回落至3.5%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">如果聯儲會本月再次降息，香港的借貸成本可能會進一步下降；香港聯繫匯率制度下，本地利率與美國政策保持密切聯繫。美元需求疲軟也可能推高港元兌美元匯率，使其突破7.75-7.85交易區間的強方兌換保證水平，促使香港金管局拋售港元，從而進一步提振流動性。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6df29314-3ec5-3b5a-9456-4f592d88dc71-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sAl5YYxnvUkRT6nn3YE_3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ca33892ff95b52a25b3ffdd4a9fad86c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">華僑銀行經濟學家Cindy Keung表示，隨著聯儲會繼續降息，預計1個月和3個月期Hibor未來幾個月將逐步走低，到年底前將回落至接近3%的水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她預期貸款需求的復甦有限，不足以推動Hibor大幅上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hong Kong Funding Cost to Drop Near 3% on Fed Cuts, Slow Lending</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Dave Sebastian.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%9A%94%E5%A4%9C%E8%9E%8D%E8%B3%87%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E9%99%8D%E8%87%B33-%E5%9B%A0%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%8F%8A%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E6%94%BE%E7%B7%A9-232035920.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-03 10:05:58",
